# SOLEMATE

SOLEMATE (SM.CO) is a complete e-commerce website for premium footwear. The site features a modern, responsive design with a unique AI-powered shoe matching experience called "Find Your Solemate" - think Tinder for shoes! Built with semantic HTML and modular CSS, ready to be extended with backend functionality.

## ğŸ¯ Core Features

### Homepage (`index.html`)
- **Promotional Bar**: Eye-catching announcement bar with "FIND YOUR SOLEMATE" message
- **Hero Section**: Bold value proposition with call-to-action and social proof metrics
- **Brand Showcase**: Featured brand logos strip (Nike, Adidas, Puma, Versace, Gucci, Prada)
- **Product Sections**:
  - New Arrivals: Grid layout with product cards
  - Top Selling: Featured products with ratings and pricing
  - Latest Drops: Showcase layout for curated collections
- **Browse by Style**: Masonry grid with hover effects (Casual, Formal, Party, Gym)
- **Find Your Solemate Promo**: Interactive showcase with animated phone mockup
- **Customer Testimonials**: Carousel-ready reviews section
- **Newsletter Signup**: Email capture with engaging CTA
- **Footer**: Comprehensive links with social media and payment icons

### Find Your Solemate (`html/find-solemate.html`) ğŸ”¥
Our signature feature - a Tinder-style shoe matching experience:
- **Hero Section**: Feature introduction with compelling copy
- **Preferences Panel**:
  - Gender selection (Men, Women, Unisex)
  - Shoe size selector
  - Style preferences (Casual, Sporty, Formal, Streetwear, Luxury)
  - Price range slider
  - Color picker with swatches
- **Swipe Interface**:
  - Stacked card design with preview layers
  - Detailed product cards with images, descriptions, and ratings
  - Pass, Info, and Like action buttons
  - Match counter showing available shoes
- **How It Works**: 4-step visual guide explaining the matching process

### Shopping Pages
- **Shop (`html/shop.html`)**: Main product catalog with advanced filtering
- **On Sale (`html/on-sale.html`)**: Discounted items showcase
- **New Arrivals (`html/new-arrivals.html`)**: Latest product releases
- **Brands (`html/brands.html`)**: Brand directory with featured logos

### Brand-Specific Pages
Individual shopping pages for each premium brand:
- **Nike** (`html/nike.html`)
- **Adidas** (`html/adidas.html`)
- **Puma** (`html/puma.html`)
- **Versace** (`html/versace.html`)
- **Gucci** (`html/gucci.html`)
- **Prada** (`html/prada.html`)

Each brand page features:
- Pre-filtered product grid
- Brand-specific collection title
- Locked brand filter in sidebar
- Full filtering capabilities (category, price, size)

### Product Detail Page (`html/product.html`)
- Product image gallery with thumbnail navigation
- Product information (title, price, rating)
- Color and size selectors with visual swatches
- Quantity controls and Add to Cart button
- Tabbed content section:
  - Product Details (materials, fit, care)
  - Rating & Reviews with customer testimonials
  - FAQs accordion
- "You Might Also Like" recommendations
- Breadcrumb navigation

### Shopping Cart (`html/cart.html`)
- Cart items list with:
  - Product images and details
  - Size and color information
  - Quantity controls
  - Individual item removal
- Order Summary with:
  - Subtotal calculation
  - Discount application
  - Delivery fee
  - Total amount
  - Promo code input
  - Checkout button

### User Profile (`html/profile.html`)
- Account management interface
- Order history section
- Wishlist/favorites
- Profile settings

